32
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,320
Thank you.

33
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:32,760
How was today?

34
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,200
You skipped your work.

35
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:36,620
