47
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:05,740
I can't believe it.

48
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,280
I told you, I'm his favorite.

49
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:09,720
I want to go.

50
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,820
Can you go with me?

51
00:07:16,340 --> 00:07:17,220
Please.

52
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,980
