55
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,560
Please go.

56
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,560
I want to.

57
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,000
Ok.

58
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:39,240
Yay.

59
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:41,980
