116
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,360
Hurry up.

117
00:12:01,260 --> 00:12:01,940
Dream.

118
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:07,620
Can you help me with something?

119
00:12:09,340 --> 00:12:10,100
