124
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,380
I think I like Night.

125
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,380
Really?

126
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,620
Be quiet.

127
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,760
I'm happy for you.

128
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,320
