202
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,720
I think he just plays dump.

203
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:02,920
Namwan.

204
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,520
Wanna have dinner?

205
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:10,480
